tool_description: Nutrifai food image detection API enables you to extract the nutrition value of the foods on your table. API endpoints works asynchronously as it is using heavy ML processing to detect foods in the picture. For this purpose you need to upload your image and query results by another endpoint.
name: Food Image Detection
title: Food Image Detection

api_list.description: Get the nutrition values of extracted foods in the image.
